2064.subject: HPWE
2064.descrlong: A cardiovascular and muscular endurance workout.  Using flotation devices,  follows the instructor through a wide variety of movements using the water as resistance.  No experience in swimming necessary.  Good for people looking for an alternative to weight bearing exercise.
